      <title>自脱欧以来，维萨卡和万事达卡费用上涨了五倍，英国提议对部分卡费设置上限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/uk-proposes-capping-some-visa-mastercard-fees-after-fivefold-jump-since-brexit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国监管机构正在考虑对 Visa Inc. 和 Mastercard Inc. 向当地商户收取的每笔银行卡交易收取的部分费用设定上限，试图控制自英国脱欧以来已上涨五倍的费用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/uk-proposes-capping-some-visa-mastercard-fees-after-fivefold-jump-since-brexit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 12:15:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
