    <item>
      <title>苹果和谷歌应用商店之争的下一步是什么</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/what-s-next-in-the-fight-over-apple-and-google-s-app-stores</link>
      <description><![CDATA[陪审团花了不到四个小时就发现 Alphabet Inc. 旗下的谷歌在其 Android 应用商店中不公平地行使垄断权力，《堡垒之夜》制造商 Epic Games Inc. 以闪电般的速度获胜，这促使人们努力遏制谷歌和竞争对手苹果公司的权力。掌控移动生态系统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/what-s-next-in-the-fight-over-apple-and-google-s-app-stores</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟达成协议迫使 Uber、Deliveroo 将部分司机视为员工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/eu-deal-to-make-uber-deliveroo-treat-some-drivers-as-employees</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟谈判代表支持一项协议，将数以百万计的打车和送餐应用程序工作人员重新归类为雇员，制定的一系列规则可能每年给该行业造成数十亿欧元的损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/eu-deal-to-make-uber-deliveroo-treat-some-drivers-as-employees</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 09:52:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
